[{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0061","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0061.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1714","title":"Joomla 组件 Arcade Games 1.0 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! Arcade Games 组件 1.0 版本存在目录遍历漏洞，攻击者可通过 index.php 的 controller 参数传入目录遍历序列（../）读取服务器任意文件。该漏洞影响 Joomla! 使用 com_arcadegames 1.0 组件的站点，远程未授权攻击者可直接通过构造恶意 controller 参数实现任意文件读取，CVSS 评分 5.0（中危），属于 CWE-22 路径遍历类漏洞。攻击者无需认证即可利用 controller 参数中的目录遍历序列读取服务器敏感文件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1714"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-05-04T16:00:36.027","updated":"2026-06-16T23:19:10.747","remediation":"建议将 Arcade Games (com_arcadegames) 组件升级至官方修复目录遍历问题的版本；若该组件已停止维护，应在 Joomla 后台扩展管理中直接卸载或禁用该组件。临时缓解措施：在 Web 服务器（如 Apache/Nginx）层部署过滤规则，拦截 index.php 的 controller 参数中包含 ../ 或 .. 的请求，或使用 ModSecurity 等 WAF 规则阻止路径穿越字符，并限制 Web 目录文件读取权限以减小信息泄露风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlaarcadegames-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39413","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12168","http://www.osvdb.org/63660","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2010/0860","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/57683","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12168","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1714.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2010/POC-AVE-2010-0061.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0061.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0060","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0060.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1659","title":"Joomla! Ultimate Portfolio 组件 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! CMS 旗下 Ultimate Portfolio 1.0 组件存在目录遍历漏洞，攻击者可通过向 index.php 发起请求时在控制器参数中嵌入 '..' 路径穿越序列，绕过验证访问服务器上任意文件。该漏洞影响 Joomla! 用户，导致敏感信息泄露。漏洞因可读取文件而具备安全风险，CVSS 评分 5.0，等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1659"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-05-03T13:51:53.277","updated":"2026-06-16T23:18:48.237","remediation":"立即卸载或禁用 Joomla! Ultimate Portfolio 组件（com_ultimateportfolio）1.0 版本，该组件已停止维护无官方补丁。若必须保留，请在 index.php 中对 controller 参数实施严格白名单校验，仅允许字母数字下划线，拦截包含 ../ 或 ..\\ 的请求。同时在 Web 应用防火墙（WAF）配置规则阻断路径遍历载荷，并限制 PHP open_basedir 目录防止跨目录读取敏感文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlaultimateportfolio-lfi.txt","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12426","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39739","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2010/1008","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/58177","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12426","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1659.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/2010/CVE-2010-1659.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/6bfef5eb290cbfeb2b2cb4d2bae8e5cab0243137/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1659.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-1659.js","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/7691a973a12bba26b673ab9d7832b4240427e043/CVE-2010/CVE-2010-16xx/CVE-2010-1659.json","https://github.com/amad3us47/amad3us47.github.io/blob/07cfc0edf465277028554b47198f6f186d3215b6/data/cve-2010-1659-1770.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/33f1cec9d77d251a92ed8670e1fe74e3e6358e2a/cves/2010/1xxx/CVE-2010-1659.json","https://github.com/gongzeq/VAPT3/blob/3576a7accf5cbadc8e64924d6ff48393db379ea7/secbot/resource/poc/cve/cve-2010-1659-1772.yaml","https://github.com/rxerium/CISA-KEV/blob/84704a4e12b7141ddbae43e4ee4ff4d8d0e3ee70/data/lists/NucleiList.txt","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-1659_32.yaml","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2010-1659-1771.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0060.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0059","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0059.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1658","title":"Joomla! Code-Garage NoticeBoard 1.3 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Code-Garage NoticeBoard（com_noticeboard）组件 1.3 版本存在目录遍历漏洞，攻击者可通过对 index.php 中的 controller 参数传入 '..' 路径序列遍历访问控制权限，未经身份认证的远程用户可读取服务器上的任意文件（如配置文件、敏感源码）。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1658"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-05-03T13:51:53.247","updated":"2026-06-16T23:18:48.123","remediation":"升级 Joomla! 到 3.10.13 及以上版本或 4.x 系列，或移除已废弃的 NoticeBoard 组件。进一步的安全措施包括应用安全补丁、限制文件权限、禁用目录遍历功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlnoticeboard-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39600","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12427","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39742","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2010/1007","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/58176"],"poc_urls":["http://localhost/index.php?option=com_noticeboard&controller=../../../../../../../../../etc/passwd%00"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0059.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0057","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0057.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1653","title":"Joomla! 组件 Graphics 1.0.6 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! Graphics 组件（com_graphics）1.0.6 和 1.5.0 版本的 graphics.php 文件存在目录遍历漏洞，攻击者可通过向 index.php 的 controller 参数传递 '..' 等目录遍历序列，包含并执行任意本地文件。该漏洞源于对用户输入的 controller 参数缺乏路径规范化校验，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，通过目录遍历序列突破目录限制读取或执行服务器本地敏感文件，可能导致敏感信息泄露或远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 Joomla! 使用受影响 Graphics 组件版本的站点。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1653"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-05-03T13:51:53.057","updated":"2026-06-16T23:18:47.567","remediation":"立即将 Joomla! 的 Graphics (com_graphics) 组件升级至 1.5.1 或更高版本以获取补丁修复。若官方已停止维护，请通过后台「扩展管理」中直接卸载或禁用该组件。同时可在 Web 服务器（如 Apache/Nginx）层添加规则过滤请求路径中的 '../'、编码穿越字符，并限制 index.php 的 controller 参数仅允许白名单取值，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlagraphics-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39585","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12430","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39743","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2010/1004","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12430","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1653.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-1653.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1653.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-1653.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2010-1653-1757.yaml","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder3/cve-2010-1653-1755.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-1653_26.yaml","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2022/Nov/20/lfiArtifact/lfiReport.csv","https://github.com/mscandev/mscan/blob/cb7ba038f76e6e0cf8ffa6ab00db702265d3191c/web/nuclei-templates/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1653.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-1653-1756.yaml","https://github.com/cckuailong/reapoc/blob/699762e4c31d0183733f64313d8fc3be6470bd37/2010/README.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0057.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0055","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0055.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1603","title":"Joomla! 组件 ZiMBCore 0.1 - 局部文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 ZiMBCore（com_zimbcore）组件 0.1 版本存在目录穿越漏洞。该组件在处理 index.php 的 controller 参数时未对用户输入进行充分过滤，远程攻击者可构造包含 `..`（点点）序列的恶意请求，绕过路径限制读取服务器上的任意文件（如配置文件、敏感源码等）。由于 Joomla! 通常部署于公开 Web 服务器，任何未经过身份认证的远程用户只要能访问目标站点即可发起攻击，无需特殊权限或前置条件，攻击门槛较低。利用方式简单，仅需向 index.php 发送带有恶意 controller 参数的 HTTP 请求即可触发，除任意文件读取外还可能造成其他未明确的影响，属于高危信息泄露类漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1603"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-04-29T17:30:00.683","updated":"2026-06-16T23:18:41.490","remediation":"建议立即卸载或禁用 Joomla! ZiMBCore 0.1 组件，或升级至 ZiMB Manager 系列最新版本。临时缓解措施：在 Web 应用防火墙层面拦截包含目录遍历序列（../）的 controller 参数请求，或在 Joomla 后台禁用 com_zimbcore 组件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlazimbmanager-lfi.txt","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12284","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39546","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2010/0931","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12284","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1603.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-1603.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1603.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-1603.js","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-1603-1748.yaml","https://github.com/cyb3r-w0lf/nuclei-template-collection/blob/7025ebe04ab60b84aee0af1ecf4f90601332e8e7/nuclei-templates/CVE-2010/cve-2010-1603.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/97a1d197a6d2b1e5c4bff302e1cddaad419096dc/cves/2010/1xxx/CVE-2010-1603.json","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2022/Dec/04/lfiArtifact/lfiReport.csv","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-1603_7.yaml","https://github.com/emadshanab/nucleiDB/blob/a06eb8edf2853662c304e3f41f8887b65f56e399/z-11753.yaml","https://github.com/GhostTroops/scan4all/blob/fff03b51bf79c8993a46c1da766ec993e1102c47/config/51pwn/yaml/Joomla/CVE-2010-1603.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0055.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0050","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0050.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1535","title":"Joomla! TRAVELbook 组件 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 TRAVELbook（com_travelbook）组件 1.0.1 版本存在目录遍历（本地文件包含）漏洞，其根源在于组件在处理 index.php 的 controller 参数时未对用户输入进行充分的路径过滤与校验。远程、无需身份认证的攻击者可通过向 index.php 提交包含“../”（点点）序列的恶意 controller 参数，突破目录限制读取服务器上的任意文件（如配置文件、源代码、敏感凭证等）。该漏洞影响安装并启用了 TRAVELbook 1.0.1 组件的 Joomla! 网站，攻击仅需构造特制 URL 发起 HTTP 请求即可，可造成敏感信息泄露，并可能被进一步利用产生其他未明影响。建议用户及时升级或停用存在漏洞的组件。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1535"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-04-26T18:30:00.753","updated":"2026-06-16T23:18:34.427","remediation":"建议立即升级 Joomla! TRAVELbook 组件至 1.0.2 或更高版本，官方已修复该目录遍历漏洞。若暂时无法升级，可在 Joomla 后台禁用 com_travelbook 组件，或在 Web 应用防火墙配置规则拦截包含 \"../\" 等目录遍历序列的 controller 参数请求。同时建议将 PHP 配置中 open_basedir 限制在网站根目录，限制 PHP 文件读取范围作为纵深防御。建议定期检查 Joomla 官方安全公告及时更新所有扩展组件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/39254","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12151","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12151","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1535.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-1535.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1535.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/bef45ac8bcc9ee2ca44f6ae8c25801f320761c2b/cves/2010/1xxx/CVE-2010-1535.json","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2010-1535-1725.yaml","https://github.com/emadshanab/nucleiDB/blob/a06eb8edf2853662c304e3f41f8887b65f56e399/cve-2010-1535-1724.yaml","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder3/CVE-2010-1535.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-1535-1728.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-1535_7.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-1535.js","https://github.com/0isagoodnumber/nuclei_templates/blob/7399a62723d05863ea3f5c2d96b8fe71a1f0ced0/templates/CVE-2010-1535.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2010/POC-AVE-2010-0050.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2010/EXP-AVE-2010-0050.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0050.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0048","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0048.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1534","title":"Joomla Shoutbox Pro 组件目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Shoutbox Pro（com_shoutbox）组件 1.3 版本中存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 index.php 的 controller 参数传递包含 `..`（点点）的恶意路径，绕过访问控制读取服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞源于组件未对用户输入的路径参数进行充分的过滤与验证，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，结合公开的 PoC 可实现敏感信息泄露。影响范围包括使用该组件的所有 Joomla! 站点，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1534"],"sources":["nuclei"],"publish