lse,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0048.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0047","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0047.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1533","title":"Joomla! TweetLA 组件本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 TweetLA（com_tweetla）组件 1.0.1 版本中存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向 index.php 文件的 controller 参数传入包含 ..（点点）的恶意路径，实现任意文件读取，导致网站敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响运行 Joomla! CMS 并启用该组件的网站系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1533"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-04-26T18:30:00.690","updated":"2026-06-16T23:18:34.207","remediation":"立即卸载 Joomla! 后台已安装的 TweetLA 组件（com_tweetla），或在服务器上删除 components/com_tweetla/ 目录。如仍需类似功能，选择仍在维护的替代组件。同时配置 Web 应用防火墙（如 ModSecurity）拦截路径遍历特征，规则示例：`SecRule ARGS:controller \"@contains ..\" \"id:1001,deny\"`。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/39258","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12142","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12142","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1533.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-1533.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1533.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/bef45ac8bcc9ee2ca44f6ae8c25801f320761c2b/cves/2010/1xxx/CVE-2010-1533.json","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/cve-2010-1533-1715_1.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2010/CVE-2010-1533.json","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2010-1533_3.yaml","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2022/Dec/11/lfiArtifact/lfiReport.csv","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v2/C/CVE-2010-1533.yaml","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder2/cve-2010-1533-1717.yaml","https://github.com/u21h2/nacs/blob/1eaa239ded7496317a47073605c8ddda70686ef5/web/poc/pocs/nuclei/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1533.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0047.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0046","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0046.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1532","title":"Joomla! PowerMail Pro 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 PowerMail Pro 组件 1.5.3 版本中存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向 index.php 的 controller 参数中传入包含 `..`（点点）的恶意路径，实现任意文件读取。该漏洞源于程序未对用户输入的路径参数进行充分过滤，可读取系统敏感文件如配置文件等，可能导致进一步的信息泄露。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1532"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-04-26T18:30:00.660","updated":"2026-06-16T23:18:34.100","remediation":"立即在 Joomla 后台卸载 com_powermail 组件（PowerMail Pro 1.5.3），该扩展已停止维护不再有安全更新。替换为仍在维护的其他 Joomla 邮件表单扩展。若暂时无法卸载，可在 Apache/Nginx 或 WAF 层面添加规则，拦截 controller 参数中包含 `../` 或 `..%2f` 等目录遍历特征的 GET 请求，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlapowermail-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39226","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12118","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39348","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12118","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1532.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-1532.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1532.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-1532.js","h