mko 组件 1.01 版本存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过在 index.php 的 controller 参数中传入 ../ 序列实现路径穿越，越权读取服务器上的任意文件，包括配置文件、数据库凭据等敏感信息，可能导致服务器完全沦陷。该漏洞影响 Joomla! 上运行的 Matamko 组件 1.01 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1495"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-04-23T14:30:01.417","updated":"2026-06-16T23:18:29.850","remediation":"立即卸载 com_matamko 组件（Joomla! 后台 → 扩展管理 → 管理 → 找到 Matamko 点击卸载）；若必须保留业务功能，则修改组件入口文件，对 controller 参数做白名单校验，仅允许字母数字控制器名，同时过滤 `../` 和 `%00` 等目录遍历字符，并配置 WAF 规则拦截包含 `controller=../` 的 URL 请求。版本已无法获取官方更新，卸载是最彻底方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/63918","http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlamatamko-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39523","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12286","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39550","http://www.vupen.com/english/advisories/2010/0929","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12286","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1495.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-1495.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1495.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-1495.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2010-1495-1699.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/bef45ac8bcc9ee2ca44f6ae8c25801f320761c2b/cves/2010/1xxx/CVE-2010-1495.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-1495_49.yaml","https://github.com/emadshanab/nucleiDB/blob/a06eb8edf2853662c304e3f41f8887b65f56e399/cve-2010-1495-1699.yaml","https://github.com/EMBA-support-repos/EPSS-data/blob/c550310f32d73cc607c18f8598a32c323f1d023a