cus.com/bid/39607","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12318","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1491.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-1491.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1491.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-1491.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2010-1491-1693.yaml","https://github.com/wpsec/ARL-Source-Install/blob/aecf83f1f55a6f1a1a67dbe25e22ea0eb5a44bf2/tools/nuclei-templates/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1491.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-1491_11.yaml","https://github.com/westonsteimel/national-vulnerability-database/blob/2ce54d3744fd5bcac7a1e8c5fe748135d72fb2a6/data/2010/CVE-2010-1491.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dirtra.txt","https://github.com/Ciyfly/woodpecker/blob/f88bed6da55238547a423ce17dccb2cdbc93be50/pocs/nuclei/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1491.yaml","https://github.com/exploit-io/nuclei-templates/blob/a4b7182985a6e45df346cfe45242d40455e152b5/templates/cve-2010-1491-1689.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0042.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0041","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0041.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1478","title":"Joomla! Jfeedback 组件目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Jfeedback 组件 1.2 版本存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过在 controller 参数中注入 `../` 序列，进而读取服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞影响使用该组件的所有 Joomla! 站点，CVSS 评分 6.8，危害等级中危。由于缺少对用户输入的充分过滤，攻击者可获取敏感配置文件或系统文件，可能导致进一步的信息泄露或攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1478"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-04-19T19:30:01.007","updated":"2026-06-16T23:18:28.283","remediation":"建议立即在 Joomla! 后台扩展管理器中卸载 com_jfeedback 组件，或从服务器删除该组件目录。如无法卸载，修改 PHP 代码在 controller 参数入口处过滤 ../ 和 %00 字符，仅允许字母数字和白名单值；同时在 Apache/Nginx 层添加 RewriteRule/location 规则拦截包含目录遍历特征的请求，并将 PHP 配置 open_basedir 限制到站点根目录以阻止读取系统文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlajfeedback-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39262","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12145","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39390","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12145","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1478.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-1478.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1478.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-1478.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2010-1478-1687.yaml","https://github.com/GhostTroops/scan4all/blob/fff03b51bf79c8993a46c1da766ec993e1102c47/config/51pwn/CVE-2010-1478.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/bef45ac8bcc9ee2ca44f6ae8c25801f320761c2b/cves/2010/1xxx/CVE-2010-1478.json","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2010-1478_3.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-1478_36.yaml","https://github.com/0xelixer/new/blob/6f6dd4a43a76ce74c1e8cc0558629a2ea198286e/nuclei-temps/cent/template1/cve-2010-1478-1688.yaml","https://github.com/Jimi-Lab/workflow/blob/64e0ded287550d9a2309e6b5a8188e373d9e88ca/VulnVersion/DataSet/CveDetail/CVE-2022-0995/cxsecurity/list.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0041.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0040","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0040.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-1476","title":"Joomla! AlphaUserPoints 组件 1.5.5 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 AlphaUserPoints 组件 1.5.5 版本存在目录遍历漏洞（CWE-22）。远程攻击者可通过向 index.php 的 view 参数传入 `../` 序列绕过路径限制，实现任意文件读取，可能进一步导致敏感信息泄露或其他未明影响。该漏洞利用难度低，无需身份认证即可触发，影响运行该组件的 Joomla! 站点。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.8,"aliases":["CVE-2010-1476"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-04-19T19:30:00.947","updated":"2026-06-16T23:18:28.053","remediation":"立即升级 AlphaUserPoints 组件至官方最新版本（高于 1.5.5），或在 Joomla! 后台卸载 com_alphauserpoints 组件以彻底消除风险。如因业务必须保留，可修改 controller.php 中对 view 参数的取值逻辑，过滤 `../` 等目录穿越字符，并限制 view 参数仅允许字母数字和白名单路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1004-exploits/joomlaalphauserpoints-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/39250","http://www.alphaplug.com/","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12150","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/39393","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/12150","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1476.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-1476.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-1476.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-1476.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2010-1476-1679.yaml","https://github.com/emadshanab/nucleiDB/blob/a06eb8edf2853662c304e3f41f8887b65f56e399/cve-2010-1476-16